{"id":240,"date":"2019-03-17T16:12:05","date_gmt":"2019-03-17T09:12:05","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/tppone.com\/demo\/edu5\/?p=240"},"modified":"2019-03-17T17:37:53","modified_gmt":"2019-03-17T10:37:53","slug":"langmaster-international-fair-ngay-hoi-soi-dong-cua-gioi-tre","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/edu5.websiteviet.vn\/tin-tuc\/langmaster-international-fair-ngay-hoi-soi-dong-cua-gioi-tre\/","title":{"rendered":"Langmaster International Fair &#8211; ng\u00e0y h\u1ed9i s\u00f4i \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u1ee7a gi\u1edbi tr\u1ebb"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><strong>T\u1ea1i h\u1ed9i tr\u1ea1i Langmaster International Fair 2018, sinh vi\u00ean \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tham gia ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng giao l\u01b0u, t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u v\u0103n h\u00f3a \u0111\u1ec3 trau d\u1ed3i kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng th\u1ef1c h\u00e0nh ti\u1ebfng Anh.<\/strong><\/p>\n<p>Nh\u1eb1m gi\u00fap h\u1ecdc vi\u00ean l\u00e0m ch\u1ee7 ti\u1ebfng Anh nh\u01b0 ng\u00f4n ng\u1eef th\u1ee9 2, Langmaster lu\u00f4n tham kh\u1ea3o c\u00e1c m\u00f4 h\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o v\u00e0 s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o th\u00eam nhi\u1ec1u ph\u01b0\u01a1ng th\u1ee9c hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3. H\u1ec7 sinh th\u00e1i h\u1ecdc ti\u1ebfng Anh to\u00e0n di\u1ec7n 4CE c\u1ee7a Langmaster g\u1ed3m: class (l\u1edbp h\u1ecdc), club (c\u00e2u l\u1ea1c b\u1ed9), e-study (c\u1ed5ng h\u1ecdc vi\u00ean), community (ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u1ed9ng \u0111\u1ed3ng), conference (h\u1ed9i th\u1ea3o v\u1edbi chuy\u00ean gia). Trong \u0111\u00f3, Langmaster International Fair 2018 l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ecdc vi\u00ean r\u00e8n luy\u1ec7n kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng th\u1ef1c h\u00e0nh Anh ng\u1eef, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 n\u1ec1n v\u0103n h\u00f3a c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c n\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u00ean th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi.<\/p>\n<p>V\u1edbi m\u00f4 h\u00ecnh thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y h\u1ed9i l\u1edbn, s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n n\u00e0y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i giao l\u01b0u, k\u1ebft n\u1ed1i gi\u1ea3ng vi\u00ean, tr\u1ee3 gi\u1ea3ng v\u1edbi c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc vi\u00ean c\u00f9ng nhi\u1ec1u ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng th\u00fa v\u1ecb nh\u01b0 h\u1ed9i tr\u1ea1i, ch\u1ee3 t\u1eeb thi\u1ec7n, c\u00e1c gameshow v\u00e0 ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng bi\u1ec3u di\u1ec5n v\u0103n ngh\u1ec7. \u0110\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng tri \u00e2n \u0111\u00e1nh d\u1ea5u ch\u1eb7ng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng 7 n\u0103m ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n c\u1ee7a trung t\u00e2m. S\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n thu \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1eeb ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng mua b\u00e1n, kinh doanh trong h\u1ed9i ch\u1ee3 s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi c\u00e1c em nh\u1ecf v\u00f9ng cao kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n trong T\u1ebft 2019.<\/p>\n<div>V\u1edbi s\u1ef1 tham d\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a g\u1ea7n 600 h\u1ecdc vi\u00ean, 24 gian tr\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n cho 24 qu\u1ed1c gia. C\u00e1c h\u1ecdc vi\u00ean c\u0169ng chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb b\u00e0i thuy\u1ebft tr\u00ecnh ng\u1eafn v\u1ec1 v\u0103n h\u00f3a c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 \u0111\u1eb7c tr\u01b0ng c\u1ee7a qu\u1ed1c gia m\u00ecnh ch\u1ecdn.<\/div>\n<p>V\u0169 \u0110\u1ee9c Trung (\u0110H B\u00e1ch khoa H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i) chia s\u1ebb: \u201c\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 d\u1ecbp \u0111\u1ec3 sinh vi\u00ean b\u1ecdn m\u00ecnh giao l\u01b0u, trao \u0111\u1ed5i b\u1eb1ng ti\u1ebfng Anh, t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 c\u00e1c n\u1ec1n v\u0103n h\u00f3a kh\u00e1c nhau tr\u00ean th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi nh\u01b0 M\u1ef9, Ai C\u1eadp, Canada, Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n\u2026 \u0110\u00e2y c\u00f2n l\u00e0 cu\u1ed9c thi n\u00ean m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi r\u1ea5t h\u00e0o h\u1ee9ng tham gia\u201d.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>T\u1ea1i h\u1ed9i tr\u1ea1i Langmaster International Fair 2018, sinh vi\u00ean \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tham gia ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng giao l\u01b0u, t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u v\u0103n h\u00f3a \u0111\u1ec3 trau d\u1ed3i kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng th\u1ef1c h\u00e0nh ti\u1ebfng Anh. Nh\u1eb1m gi\u00fap h\u1ecdc vi\u00ean l\u00e0m ch\u1ee7 ti\u1ebfng Anh nh\u01b0 ng\u00f4n ng\u1eef th\u1ee9 2, Langmaster lu\u00f4n tham kh\u1ea3o c\u00e1c m\u00f4 h\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o v\u00e0 s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o&#8230;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":241,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":[7],"tags":[8],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/edu5.websiteviet.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/240"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/edu5.websiteviet.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/edu5.websiteviet.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/edu5.websiteviet.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/edu5.websiteviet.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=240"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https:\/\/edu5.websiteviet.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/240\/revisions"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/edu5.websiteviet.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/241"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/edu5.websiteviet.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=240"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/edu5.websiteviet.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=240"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/edu5.websiteviet.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=240"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}